      <h2 class="title">
      <a href="/node/154" title="Access CICS applications with Spring">Access CICS applications with Spring</a>
    </h2>
  
  
      <div class="meta">
              <div class="submitted">
          Submitted by Dmitriy Kopylenko on Mon, 2005-08-22 10:09        </div>
      
              <div class="terms terms-inline"> in <ul class="links inline"><li class="taxonomy_term_6 first last active"><a href="/presentations" rel="tag" title="A link to a technical article about Spring" class="active">Technical Article</a></li>
</ul></div>
          </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>Thierry Templier has written an article about accessing IBM's CICS mainframe applications using J2CA resource adapters and Spring's CCI support subsystem. <a target="_blank" href="http://www.javaworld.com/javaworld/jw-08-2005/jw-0822-cics.html">Read</a> the article here.</p>
  </div>

