      <h2 class="title">
      <a href="/node/142" title="Article: Spring 1.2’s Java 5 Based Transaction Annotations">Article: Spring 1.2’s Java 5 Based Transaction Annotations</a>
    </h2>
  
  
      <div class="meta">
              <div class="submitted">
          Submitted by Colin Sampaleanu on Fri, 2005-07-22 15:25        </div>
      
              <div class="terms terms-inline"> in <ul class="links inline"><li class="taxonomy_term_6 first last active"><a href="/presentations" rel="tag" title="A link to a technical article about Spring" class="active">Technical Article</a></li>
</ul></div>
          </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    In <a href="http://blog.exis.com/colin/archives/2005/07/18/spring-12s-java-5-based-transaction-annotations/" target="_self">Spring 1.2&rsquo;s Java 5 Based Transaction Annotations</a>, I give an
overview of the Java 5+ compatible transaction Annotations that were
officially introduced with Spring 1.2.<br />
