</ul></div>
          </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p><a href="http://tahe.developpez.com/java/swing3tier/" target="_self">Construction d'une application swing MVC &agrave; trois couches avec Spring</a> (which roughly translates to &quot;Construction of a three layer MVC 
swing application with Spring&quot;) is a comprehensive (49 page) article by Serge Tahé, in French.</p>  </div>

